\c 57 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 57\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Rakkina Keessatti Kooluu Argatanii Galateeffachuu (Geggeessituu warra faarfatootaaf; kun akka qooqa faarfannaa isa "Hin balleessin" jedhamuutti faarfatame; kan Daawit, isa afaan Ibrootaatti "Mikitaam" jedhamuu dha; Daawit yeroo Saa'ol jalaa baqatee holqa dhagaatti gale kana faarfate)
\m \bd 1\bd* Araara anatti argisiisi, yaa Waaqayyo! Lubbuun koo kooluu waan sitti galteef, araara anatti argisiisi! Badiisi jabaan hamma darbutti, ani gaaddisa bobaa kee jalatti kooluu nan gala. 
\m \bd 2\bd* Waaqayyo isa hundumaa gararraatti, Waaqayyo isa dubbii koo anaaf raawwatutti nan iyyadha.
\m \bd 3\bd* Nama arrabsee na ari'u jalaa na oolchuudhaaf, inni waaqa irraa in erga; Waaqayyo gaarummaa isaa fi amanamummaa isaa in erga.
\m \bd 4\bd* Warra akka leencaa nama nyaachuu kajeelanii ija isaanii bobeessan gidduu nan ciisa; ilkaan isaanii akka eeboo fi akka xiyyaa ti, arrabni isaaniis akka billaa qaramaa ti.
\m \bd 5\bd* Bantiiwwan waaqaa gararraatti ol ka'i, yaa Waaqayyo! Ulfinni kees lafa hundumaa irratti ol haa jedhu!
\m \bd 6\bd* Warri sun miilla koo dura futtaasaa dhaaban, lubbuun koos gadditee gad deebite; boolla anaaf qotan, ofuma isaaniitii immoo walakkaa isaatti kufan.
\m \bd 7\bd* Garaan koo hin shakku, yaa Waaqayyo! Garaan koo hin shakku; sin faarfadha, sagalee mi'a garaa garaas nan dhageessisa.
\m \bd 8\bd* Yaa lubbuu ko dammaqi, yaa kiraaraa, yaa maseenqoo, dammaqaa! Ani barii lafaa nan dammaqsa.
\m \bd 9\bd* Ani namoota keessatti sin galateeffadha, yaa gooftaa, saba lafa irraa keessattis faarfannaadhaan sin jajadha.
\m \bd 10\bd* gaarummaan kee hamma bantii waaqaatti in guddata, amanamummaan kees hamma duumessaa in ga'a.
\m \bd 11\bd* Bantiiwwan waaqaa gararraatti ol ka'i, yaa Waaqayyo! Ulfinni kees lafa hundumaa irratti ol haa jedhu!
